      "text": "Therefore:"
    }
,    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "4158064554893027",
      "text": "Refactor the model to separate the [[core domain]] concepts from supporting players (including ill-defined ones) and strengthen the cohesion of the [[core domain]] while reducing its coupling to other code. Factor all generic or supporting elements into other objects and place them into other packages, even if this means refactoring the model in ways that separate highly coupled elements."
